data.description: NOTE:  Professional pictures coming soon.  Don't let this stop you - it shows beautifully!      Open & airy home on 1 acre in a picturesque neighborhood.  Conveniently located minutes from U.S. 1. The exterior stone and brick masonry is one of a kind along with a fabulous front porch made for rocking. This home also features a gourmet kitchen with granite countertops, 42''custom cabinets, breakfast bar, and 3 large pantries just to name a few of the amenities.  The entertaining space flows into a bright family room with custom fireplace and mantle and panoramic views of your private, wooded backyard. Rich oak hardwood flooring flows throughout the main floor. Custom crown molding and arch doorways complete the polished look and feel of this home. Special occasions will be cherished in your elegant dining room highlighting coffered ceilings. All spacious bedrooms are located upstairs along with a large laundry room featuring custom built-in shelving. Coming home to your oversized and peaceful master suite is a treat.  It feels like a treehouse with the wooded views. You will love the trey ceilings, master ensuite with separate shower and garden tub, double sinks, private loo and walk-in closet with custom shelving. There is tons of storage available in the third story attic.  This home is a must see in the growing town of Franklinton.
